Intelligent Analytics Apps

Manage Your Intelligent Apps

Use the App Management tab to manage Intelligent Apps, such as Revenue Intelligence, Commerce Intelligence, or Service Intelligence. Monitor the status of installs, view logs for troubleshooting install issues, update and delete apps, and schedule app refreshes.

Installed versions display as separate tabs. Select an app tab to view details: installation status, events, and tasks. Schedule app refreshes or refresh manually and see all installed resources like dashboards and data transforms.

Monitor, Update, and Delete Intelligent Apps
Change Your Intelligent App Settings
View Your Intelligent App Resources
Troubleshoot Your Intelligent Apps

You can change settings for your Intelligent App, such as instantly refreshing the app or scheduling an app refresh to be performed later.
See and explore the resources your Intelligent App installs, including Einstein Studio models, CRM Analytics dashboards, recipes, and datasets, and Data Cloud transforms and data model objects.

Cancel running installations, view logs and state of an Intelligent App, and troubleshoot problems.
title: Managing Salesforce Intelligent Apps
